title: Maracattack
description:
This was not my rip, but the only torrent I could find, this has been repacked as a wmv to be playable on Xbox360

Sorry about the water marking in the top corner, I did not rip the show I just got it working for the Xbox and wanted to share.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Comedienne Miranda Hart presents this unconventional workout regime that aims to blend fun and fitness. Hart is joined for the project by guests Patricia Hodge, Sarah Hadland, Tom Ellis and Kirstie Allsopp, while fitness instructor Amelia Watts provides some direction. Alongside new comedy sketches, the programme includes a cardio workout, a higher intensity cardio workout, strengthening exercises for the arms, core, legs and buttocks and a relaxation session. The emphasis is on fun throughout and the workouts are performed to some cheesy pop classics.
